channel.title: AGSPking Version TWO!(2) Worth a look!
channel.description:
Hi guys, Noobie22 again. Here with VERSION 2!
First off, I'd like to thank Faded Vision for his base, PwnScape 3.
Let's get down to business!
Donator ONLY shop [IMG]http://i703.photobucket.com/albums/ww39/Pker4fun96/0000-3.png[/img]
Staff zone! [IMG]http://i703.photobucket.com/albums/ww39/Pker4fun96/0009.png[/img]
The shops for staff [IMG]http://i703.photobucket.com/albums/ww39/Pker4fun96/0010-1.png[/img]
Real RS drops [IMG]http://i703.photobucket.com/albums/ww39/Pker4fun96/0001.png[/img]
Will post more pics later, busy ATM.
Here's the client, and source download link: http://www.mediafire.com/?zgnmyjmybyt
Credits- PEOPLE- Faded Vision-Base Noobie22-Editing, adding stuff. ______________________________________________ TuTs(Tutorials)- Rune-Serv- Requirements interface _______________________________________________
Hope you enjoy V2.
